    {
      "id": "65fccc5a-c944-4aff-8b57-84e2d6e43ab1",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Students engage in faulty learning processes all the time and it is very rare that they are “special”. So, it is possible for experienced professors to identify common wrong answers and common faulty learning processes that lead to the CWA.",
